{"word":"H8593 - תַּעַר - taʻar - tah'-ar - Knife","slug":"H8593","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">תַּעַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>taʻar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tah'-ar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Knife"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05E2;&#x05E8; - ta&#x201B;ar</b> - <i>tah'-ar</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6168\">H6168</a>; a <i>knife</i> or <i>razor</i> (as <i>making</i> bare); also a <i>scabbard</i> (as <i>being bare</i>, that is, empty): - [pen-] knife, rasor, scabbard, shave, sheath."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4626\">H4626</a>, <a href=\"#/H4629\">H4629</a>, <a href=\"#/H4638\">H4638</a>, <a href=\"#/H6168\">H6168</a>, <a href=\"#/H6169\">H6169</a>, <a href=\"#/H6171\">H6171</a>, <a href=\"#/H6172\">H6172</a>, <a href=\"#/H6181\">H6181</a>"}]}